===============================================================
[2026-03-02] DECISION #1: Multi-stage Dockerfile
===============================================================

## Options Considered
1. Separate Dockerfiles for app, celery-worker, celery-beat
2. Single multi-stage Dockerfile with targets

## Choice
Option 2 — single Dockerfile with targets

## Rationale
Reduces duplication. All services share the same base image and deps.
Docker Compose `target` directive selects the appropriate stage.

## Impact
docker-compose.yml uses `target: app`, `target: celery-worker`, `target: celery-beat`

---------------------------------------------------------------
